<h3>District Information</h3>
<p>The Chaffey Joint Union High School District has provided a quality education for high
school students in the area since 1911 and continues to try and improve its administration
constantly. Striving for unique yet quality schools, the district lives up to its own goals and
expectations of preparing students to meet or exceed academic standards while helping
students develop their own sense of responsibility and appreciate individual differences.
This district takes pride in its a wide variety of classes to provide students with the
excellent education they deserve. The Chaffey Joint Union High School District strongly
believes that nothing is more important than student learning, progress and achievement,
and works hard to deliver the best education possible.</p>

